(1, 'Jestin', 'Porter', 'G', 3, 'Senior', 22, 73.0, 180.0, 34, 34, 1149, 33.8, 176, 427, 0.412, 84, 230, 0.365, 74, 90, 0.822, 25, 72, 97, 2.9, 55, 1, 42, 57, 6, 38, 510, 15.0, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Porter__Jestin-web.jpg?width=146', 'Born March 5, 2002. Son of Jessie and Antoinette Porter. Has two siblings, Jessie and Jessica. Majoring in business. Hobbies include bowling and photography. Favorite food is tacos. Favorite movie is Fast & Furious. Favorite athlete is Kobe Bryant. Biggest role model is his mother.'),
(2, 'Essam', 'Mostafa', 'F', 44, 'Graduate Student', 25, 81.0, 250.0, 33, 33, 896, 27.2, 197, 324, 0.608, 5, 11, 0.455, 80, 128, 0.625, 111, 192, 303, 9.2, 91, 1, 40, 40, 30, 39, 479, 14.5, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/7/22/Mostafa__Essam-web-edit.jpg?width=146', 'Son of Tamer Mostafa and Nilly Sa''eed. Born August 3, 1999. Three-star player from Long Island Lutheran High School. Competed for Egypt at the U19 World Cup.'),
(3, 'Camryn', 'Weston', 'G', 24, 'Redshirt Senior', 24, 75.0, 190.0, 34, 9, 950, 27.9, 142, 342, 0.415, 37, 133, 0.278, 89, 118, 0.754, 32, 98, 130, 3.8, 84, 3, 118, 69, 3, 38, 410, 12.1, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Weston__Camryn-2_web.jpg?width=146', 'Born April 3, 2000. Son of Myra Carswell-Weston and Carl Weston. Majoring in Sports Medicine. Biggest role model is his mom. Hobbies include watching movies. Favorite food is wings and seafood. Favorite movies are Friday, Friday After Next, and Like Mike. Favorite superhero is the Flash.'),
(4, 'Jlynn', 'Counter', 'G', 2, 'Senior', 0, 75.0, 195.0, 31, 25, 849, 27.4, 118, 272, 0.434, 38, 125, 0.304, 52, 69, 0.754, 12, 117, 129, 4.2, 50, 0, 109, 45, 11, 31, 326, 10.5, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Counter__Jlynn-web.jpg?width=146', 'Earned Third Team All-State honors during a season of postgraduate basketball. Played AAU with Oklahoma Chaos.'),
(5, 'Kamari', 'Lands', 'G', 22, 'Junior', 21, 80.0, 225.0, 22, 13, 442, 20.1, 65, 179, 0.363, 30, 102, 0.294, 19, 27, 0.704, 9, 42, 51, 2.3, 34, 0, 26, 20, 6, 18, 179, 8.1, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Lands__Kamari-web.jpg?width=146', 'Son of Kristy Long and Chaka Lands. Brother to Jaraan. Born May 22, 2003. Enjoys listening to country music. His favorite athletes include LeBron James and Serena Williams. Favorite movie is Bad Boys.'),
(6, 'Torey', 'Alston', 'F', 10, 'Redshirt Freshman', 20, 80.0, 200.0, 34, 20, 681, 20.0, 77, 135, 0.57, 2, 10, 0.2, 56, 102, 0.549, 56, 120, 176, 5.2, 75, 1, 29, 42, 33, 14, 212, 6.2, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Alston__Torey-1_web.jpg?width=146', 'Son of Mike and Tina Alston. His father, Mike, played football at MTSU from 1988-89. Has three siblings: Eric, Isaiah and Laurance. Born August 14, 2004. Majoring in Sports Management. Favorite food is chicken. Favorite movie is Friday. Favorite superhero is Spiderman. Favorite athlete is Kevin Durant. Biggest role models are his parents.'),
(7, 'Justin', 'Bufford', 'G', 4, 'Senior', 23, 78.0, 190.0, 34, 34, 837, 24.6, 54, 157, 0.344, 24, 91, 0.264, 41, 67, 0.612, 30, 74, 104, 3.1, 76, 1, 31, 39, 17, 26, 173, 5.1, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Bufford__Justin-web.jpg?width=146', 'Born Justin O''Neal Bufford on January 6, 2002. Son of Beverly Smith and Tony Bufford. Has three siblings: Asia Bufford, Astrea Bogan and Thaddeus Smith. Majoring in Leisure and Sports Management. Hobbies include playing Xbox and collecting shoes. Favorite food is Rotel. Favorite movies are Maze Runner and Black Hawk Down. Favorite superhero is the Flash. Favorite athletes are Tracy McGrady, Kobe Bryant and Kevin Durant. Biggest role models are Kobe Bryant and LeBron James.'),
(8, 'Tre', 'Green', 'G', 11, 'Junior', 20, 75.0, 190.0, 31, 0, 412, 13.3, 46, 98, 0.469, 29, 72, 0.403, 19, 24, 0.792, 11, 40, 51, 1.6, 25, 0, 9, 20, 1, 6, 140, 4.5, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Green__Tre-web.jpg?width=146', 'Born May 29, 2004. Son of Calvin and Maureen Green. Has five siblings: Porsha, Autumn, Rain, Stonewall and Ares. His sister, Rain Green, plays basketball at Kansas City. Majoring in Engineering. Hobbies include hand illustrations, listening to music, Netflix binging, and NBA 2K. Favorite foods are Italian food, orange chicken, Dad''s mac and cheese, and Mom''s fried pork chops. Favorite movies include The SpongeBob Movie, Coach Carter and Juice. Favorite superhero is Batman. Favorite athletes are Ja Morant and Russell Westbrook. Biggest role models are his parents.'),
(9, 'Chris', 'Loofe', 'F', 13, 'Sophomore', 20, 83.0, 230.0, 34, 1, 461, 13.6, 52, 99, 0.525, 5, 26, 0.192, 26, 50, 0.52, 38, 78, 116, 3.4, 74, 1, 8, 33, 35, 4, 135, 4.0, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Loofe__Chris-web.jpg?width=146', 'Son of Rich and Diane Loofe. Born July 10, 2004. Has one brother, Will. Majoring in Business. Hobbies include video games and music. Favorite food is tacos. Favorite movie is The Dark Knight. Favorite athlete is Kevin Durant. Biggest role model is his dad.'),
(10, 'Jarred', 'Hall', 'F', 5, 'Sophomore', 0, 80.0, 205.0, 3, 0, 16, 5.3, 3, 3, 1.0, 2, 2, 1.0, 0, 0, 0.0, 2, 3, 5, 1.7, 1, 0, 0, 2, 1, 0, 8, 2.7, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Hall__Jarred-2_web.jpg?width=146', 'Named 2023 Class 4A Mr. Basketball and District 9-4A MVP during his senior season. Became school''s career scoring leader. McDonald''s All-America Team nominee. Top ranked player in Tennessee and No. 65 ranked player in the country by Prep Hoops. ESPN four-star recruit and ranked the 26th-best power forward in the country. Averaged 27.0 points, 9.5 rebounds and 2.5 assists through his senior campaign.'),
(11, 'Alec', 'Oglesby', 'G', 1, 'Graduate Student', 23, 77.0, 200.0, 4, 0, 30, 7.5, 2, 9, 0.222, 1, 6, 0.167, 1, 2, 0.5, 1, 1, 2, 0.5, 1, 0, 3, 1, 0, 3, 6, 1.5, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Oglesby__Alec-web.jpg?width=146', 'Son of Perryn Oglesby. Business major. Born September 13, 2001. Named a three-star recruit out of high school. Averaged 24.0 points, 5.0 rebounds and 4.0 assists as a senior. Led team to the 2018-19 Florida state championship. Collected team-best three-point field goal percentage and made three-pointers as a junior. Earned All-Gainesville and all-area honors during the 2018-19 campaign.'),
(12, 'Jacob', 'Johnson', 'G', 15, 'Redshirt Senior', 23, 77.0, 195.0, 20, 1, 194, 9.7, 10, 20, 0.5, 0, 0, 0.0, 0, 4, 0.0, 7, 18, 25, 1.3, 12, 0, 7, 3, 2, 7, 20, 1.0, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Johnson__Jacob-web.jpg?width=146', 'Son of Pashell and Arthur Johnson. Has two brothers, Jeremy and Zachary. Business major. Born June 23, 2001.'),
(13, 'Christian', 'Fussell', 'F', 7, 'Senior', 23, 82.0, 225.0, 7, 0, 36, 5.1, 2, 12, 0.167, 1, 7, 0.143, 0, 1, 0.0, 3, 4, 7, 1.0, 5, 0, 1, 2, 2, 0, 5, 0.7, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Fussell__Christian-web.jpg?width=146', 'Born Nov. 28, 2001 in Atlanta, Ga. Son of Taura and Chandra Fussell. Has one brother, Garrison, and one sister, Jailon. Major is undecided. Favorite food is fried chicken. Favorite superhero is Deadpool. Favorite movie is Friday After Next. Biggest role model and favorite athlete is Kevin Durant.'),
(14, 'Isiah', 'Lightsy', 'G', 0, 'Senior', 21, 76.0, 190.0, 5, 0, 10, 2.0, 1, 5, 0.2, 1, 4, 0.25, 0, 0, 0.0, 0, 3, 3, 0.6, 2, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 3, 0.6, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Lightsy__Isiah-web.jpg?width=146', 'Born August 14, 2003. Son of Laura and Byron Lightsy. Studying exercise science. Hobbies include playing Uno and cards. Favorite food is chicken wings. Favorite movie is The Pursuit of Happiness. Favorite superhero is Iron Man. Favorite athlete is Stephen Curry. Biggest role models are his parents.'),
(15, 'Jack', 'Jubenville', 'G', 55, 'Redshirt Junior', 22, 72.0, 180.0, 5, 0, 12, 2.4, 0, 1, 0.0, 0, 0, 0.0, 2, 3, 0.667, 0, 1, 1, 0.2, 3, 0, 4, 3, 0, 0, 2, 0.4, 'https://goblueraiders.com/images/2024/6/26/Jubenville__Jack-web.jpg?width=146', 'Born March 20, 2002. Son of Colby and Katie Jubenville. Has one sister, Mary Burke Jubenville. His father played football at Millsaps College, and his mother was a dancer at Southern Miss. Majoring in Economics. Hobbies include golfing. Favorite food is salmon. Favorite superhero is Iron Man. Favorite athlete is Derrick Henry. Biggest role model is his dad.');
